      "writtenOn": "2016-02-29T15:59:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Say something about how overlap or identical objects are handled.\n\nI’d prefer stronger semantics than what you implemented (which would make it less of a bag and more of a set).",
      "revId": "c24b0ba983be134f99fd8516b8bc859af63cb9fd",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
